trans-unit.source: Contains a variable number of arguments which are either XSLT parameters or extension objects.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en variabel antall argumenter som XSLT parametere eller utvidelsen objekter.

trans-unit.source: This class is used by the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Transform%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen brukes av den <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Transform%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.XslCompiledTransform.Transform%2A>

trans-unit.source: It allows parameters and extension objects to be invoked from within the style sheet.
trans-unit.target: Det gjør parametere og filtypen objektene som skal startes fra i stilarket.

trans-unit.source: When the parameters and objects are added to the XsltArgumentList, they are associated with a namespace qualified name and a namespace URI, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Når parametere og objekter legges til i XsltArgumentList, er de koblet til et navneområde kvalifisert navn og en navneområde-URI, henholdsvis.

trans-unit.source: The following are advantages to passing an object rather than using an embedded script such as `<msxsl:script>`: - Provides better encapsulation and reuse of classes.
trans-unit.target: Følgende er fordelene ved å sende et objekt i stedet for å bruke et innebygd skript som `<msxsl:script>`:-gir bedre innkapsling og gjenbruk av klasser.

trans-unit.source: - Allows style sheets to be smaller and more easily maintained.
trans-unit.target: -Tillater stilark skal mindre og enklere opprettholdes.

trans-unit.source: - Supports passing node fragments (through the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>) to the style sheet.
trans-unit.target: -Støtter sending av noden fragmenter (via den <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>) til stilarket.</xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>

trans-unit.source: For more information about using the XsltArgumentList, see [XSLT Extension Objects](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [XSLT Parameters](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om hvordan du bruker XsltArgumentList [XSLT utvidelsen objekter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [XSLT parametere](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Implements a new instance of the <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.XsltArgumentList"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Implementerer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.XsltArgumentList"> </xref>.

trans-unit.target: Legger til et nytt objekt som den <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.XsltArgumentList"> </xref> knyttes til navneområde-URI.

trans-unit.source: The `params` keyword, which allows an unspecified number of parameters to be passed, is currently not supported.
trans-unit.target: Den `params` nøkkelord, slik at et angitt antall parametere som skal sendes, støttes ikke for øyeblikket.

trans-unit.source: XSLT style sheets that utilize methods defined with the `params` keyword does not work correctly.
trans-unit.target: XSLT-stilark som bruker metodene som er definert med den `params` nøkkelordet fungerer ikke på riktig måte.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [params](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [params](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Adds a parameter to the <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.XsltArgumentList"></xref> and associates it with the namespace qualified name.
trans-unit.target: Legger til en parameter i <xref href="System.Xml.Xsl.XsltArgumentList"> </xref> knyttes til det kvalifiserte navnet på navneområde.

trans-unit.source: The `parameter` should correspond to a W3C type.
trans-unit.target: Den `parameter` må svare til en W3C-type.

trans-unit.source: The following table shows the W3C types, either XPath or XSLT, and the corresponding.NET class.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser W3C-typer, XPath eller XSLT-filen, og corresponding.NET-klassen.

trans-unit.source: |W3C Type|Equivalent.NET Class (Type)| |--------------|-----------------------------------| |`String` (XPath)|<xref:System.String>| |`Boolean` (XPath)|<xref:System.Boolean>| |`Number` (XPath)|<xref:System.Double>| |`Result Tree Fragment` (XSLT)|<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>| |`Node Set` (XPath)|<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeIterator>
trans-unit.target: | W3C-typen | Equivalent.NET klassen (Type) | |--------------|-----------------------------------| | `String` (XPath) | <xref:System.String>| | `Boolean` (XPath) | <xref:System.Boolean>| | `Number` (XPath) | <xref:System.Double>| | `Result Tree Fragment` (XSLT)| <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>| | `Node Set` (XPath)| <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeIterator></xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeIterator></xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator></xref:System.Double></xref:System.Boolean></xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: `XPathNavigator[]`| |`Node`* (XPath)|<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>| *This is equivalent to a node set that contains a single node.
trans-unit.target: `XPathNavigator[]`| | `Node`* (XPath)|<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>| *Tilsvarer et nodesett som inneholder én enkelt node.</xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>

trans-unit.source: If the parameter object being invoked from within the style sheet is not one of the above, it is converted according to the following rules: - CLR numeric types are converted to <xref:System.Double>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis parameteren-objektet som aktiveres fra i stilarket ikke er ett av alternativene ovenfor, konverteres i henhold til følgende regler:-numerisk CLR-typer konverteres til <xref:System.Double>.</xref:System.Double>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.DateTime> type is converted to <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.DateTime>Typen er konvertert til <xref:System.String>.</xref:System.String> </xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Xml.XPath.IXPathNavigable> types are converted to <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Xml.XPath.IXPathNavigable>typer konverteres til <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>.</xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> </xref:System.Xml.XPath.IXPathNavigable>

trans-unit.source: `XPathNavigator[]` is converted to <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeIterator>.
trans-unit.target: `XPathNavigator[]`konverteres til <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeIterator>.</xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeIterator>

trans-unit.source: All other types throw an error.
trans-unit.target: Alle andre typer Iverksett en feil.
